    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
